<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrī <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> śākēbdē muniratnabhānugaṇitē vaiśākhamāsē śubhē kṛ
<lb n="2" break="no"/>ṣṇē viṣṇutithau bṛhaspatidinē śrīsi<supplied reason="omitted">ṁ</supplied>haśailēśituḥ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> śrīmajjīyyana
<lb n="3" break="no"/>dharmmadāsatanaya<supplied reason="omitted">ḥ</supplied> śrīviśvanāthaprabhurnnityaṁ svābhimatāptayē
<lb n="4"/>guṇanidhiḥ prādāt prasūnasrajaṁ <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> śrīśakavaruṣaṁbulu 1297
<lb n="5"/>gunēṁṭi vaiśākha kṛṣṇaikādaśiyu guruvāramunāṁḍu kaḷiṁgapa
<lb n="6" break="no"/>rīkṣa pātra śrīdharmmadasajīyyana koḍuku <unclear>bu</unclear>ḍayilēṁka <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> kaḷiṁgamā
<lb n="7" break="no"/>ji viśvanāthajīyyana tanaku Abhiṣṭartthasiddhagā śrīnarasiṁhanāthuni
<lb n="8" break="no"/>ki nityamunnu Oka tirumāla cātanu śrībaṁḍāramaṁduṁ padmanidhi
<lb n="9" break="no"/>gaṁḍamāḍalu Aidu veṭṭi nityamunnu kuṁcaṁḍu prasādamu vṛ
<lb n="10" break="no"/>ttigānu paḍaśi śrīkā<unclear>r</unclear>yyanāyuni Adhiṣṭānamugānu bhūmipurā
<lb n="11" break="no"/>Ikiṁ beṭṭenu Ītaṁḍu Ī prasādamu bhujiṁci nityamunnu ṟēpaṭi
<lb n="12"/>dhūpakālānanu tirumala Ātupāśi nālu mūḷlu tecci peṭṭa
<lb n="13" break="no"/>ṁgalāṁḍu Ī <supplied reason="omitted">dha</supplied>rmmu Ācaṁdrārkasthayigānu callaṁgaladu śrīvai
<lb n="14" break="no"/>ṣṇava rakṣa śrī śrī śrī
</p>

